# delegate

**Instance Property**

Specifies the notification center delegate.

## Declaration

```swift
unowned(unsafe) var delegate: (any NSUserNotificationCenterDelegate)? { get set }
```

## Discussion

The delegate must conform to the [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSUserNotificationCenterDelegate] protocol.
